---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Journey &amp; Timeline | Nazeem Massoom Dickey"
  description="How Nazeem Massoom Dickey went from zero IT background to a documented homelab, CompTIA trifecta, and SkillsUSA Florida 1st Place in under two years."
  canonical="https://masternazz.com/pages/journey.html"
>

<style is:global>
    .journey-timeline {'{'}
      position: relative;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0;
    {'}'}

    .journey-timeline::before {'{'}
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: 23px;
      top: 12px;
      bottom: 12px;
      width: 2px;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(183, 121, 255, 0.72), var(--line-strong), rgba(183, 121, 255, 0.2));
      border-radius: 2px;
    {'}'}

    .journey-entry {'{'}
      display: flex;
      gap: 28px;
      padding: 0 0 36px 0;
      position: relative;
    {'}'}

    .journey-entry:last-child {'{'}
      padding-bottom: 0;
    {'}'}

    .journey-dot {'{'}
      flex-shrink: 0;
      width: 48px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      padding-top: 18px;
    {'}'}

    .journey-dot-inner {'{'}
      width: 16px;
      height: 16px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--accent);
      border: 2px solid var(--bg);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(183, 121, 255, 0.28);
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    {'}'}

    @keyframes milestone-pulse {'{'}
      0%   {'{'} box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(183, 121, 255, 0.38), 0 0 14px rgba(183, 121, 255, 0.34); {'}'}
      50%  {'{'} box-shadow: 0 0 0 7px rgba(183, 121, 255, 0.14), 0 0 22px rgba(183, 121, 255, 0.48); {'}'}
      100% {'{'} box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(183, 121, 255, 0.38), 0 0 14px rgba(183, 121, 255, 0.34); {'}'}
    {'}'}

    .journey-entry.milestone .journey-dot-inner {'{'}
      background: var(--accent-strong);
      width: 20px;
      height: 20px;
      margin-top: -2px;
      animation: milestone-pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    {'}'}

    .journey-body {'{'}
      flex: 1;
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 18px 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 42px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18);
    {'}'}

    .journey-entry.milestone .journey-body {'{'}
      border-color: var(--line-strong);
      background: rgba(183, 121, 255, 0.07);
    {'}'}

    .journey-date {'{'}
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      color: var(--accent);
      font-size: 0.84rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    {'}'}

    .journey-entry.milestone .journey-date {'{'}
      color: var(--accent-strong);
    {'}'}

    .journey-body h3 {'{'}
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    {'}'}

    .journey-body p {'{'}
      color: var(--subtle);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 0;
    {'}'}

    .stat-strip {'{'}
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    {'}'}

    .stat-card {'{'}
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 46px var(--shadow);
    {'}'}

    .stat-card strong {'{'}
      display: block;
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--accent);
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    {'}'}

    .stat-card span {'{'}
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: var(--subtle);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    {'}'}

    @media (max-width: 820px) {'{'}
      .stat-strip {'{'}
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      {'}'}

      .journey-timeline::before {'{'}
        left: 15px;
      {'}'}

      .journey-dot {'{'}
        width: 32px;
        padding-top: 20px;
      {'}'}

      .journey-dot-inner {'{'}
        width: 12px;
        height: 12px;
      {'}'}

      .journey-entry.milestone .journey-dot-inner {'{'}
        width: 16px;
        height: 16px;
      {'}'}
    {'}'}

    @media (max-width: 500px) {'{'}
      .stat-strip {'{'}
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      {'}'}
    {'}'}
</style>

    <section class="page-hero">
      <p class="eyebrow">Personal | Career Journey</p>
      <h1>Journey &amp; Timeline</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        From zero IT background midway through junior year to a documented homelab,
        CompTIA trifecta, CySA+, and SkillsUSA Florida 1st Place — in under two years.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/pages/resume.html" class="button">Resume</a>
        <a href="/pages/homelab.html" class="button secondary">Homelab</a>
        <a href="/pages/certifications.html" class="button secondary">Certifications</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="stat-strip">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <strong><span data-countup="2" data-prefix="<" data-suffix="yr">2yr</span></strong>
          <span>Zero to documented lab</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <strong><span data-countup="3" data-suffix="wk">3wk</span></strong>
          <span>A+, Net+, Sec+ streak</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <strong><span data-countup="1" data-suffix="st">1st</span></strong>
          <span>SkillsUSA FL Internetworking</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <strong><span data-countup="31">31</span></strong>
          <span>Certifications earned</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div>
          <h2>The Full Timeline</h2>
          <p>Every step, in order — including the failed exams and the hard parts.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="journey-timeline">

        <div class="journey-entry">
          <div class="journey-dot"><div class="journey-dot-inner"></div></div>
          <div class="journey-body">
            <span class="journey-date">January 2025 – May 2026 — SouthTech Academy</span>
            <h3>Started in IT Midway Through Junior Year</h3>
            <p>Enrolled at SouthTech Academy halfway through junior year with zero IT background. First exposure was CCST Networking. Failed it twice — kept going anyway.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="journey-entry">
          <div class="journey-dot"><div class="journey-dot-inner"></div></div>
          <div class="journey-body">
            <span class="journey-date">March 2025 — First Server</span>
            <h3>IBM System x3750 — The Lab Starts</h3>
            <p>My mentor got me my first server — an IBM x3750 rackmount. No space in my room, so it lived behind a bookshelf near the router. Started experimenting with Pterodactyl, NGINX, and Minecraft hosting. First time actually seeing how services connect.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="journey-entry">
          <div class="journey-dot"><div class="journey-dot-inner"></div></div>
          <div class="journey-body">
            <span class="journey-date">September 2025 — First Rack</span>
            <h3>Synology NAS, SG300 Switch, OPNsense Optiplex</h3>
            <p>My mentor gave me a Synology NAS — first time managing real storage and backups. He and my dad helped build a two-post rack: IBM server at the bottom, NAS on the second shelf, SG300 switch on the third, and an Optiplex running OPNsense at the top with a KVM switch. First real rack.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="journey-entry milestone">
          <div class="journey-dot"><div class="journey-dot-inner"></div></div>
          <div class="journey-body">
            <span class="journey-date">Late 2025 — Turning Point</span>
            <h3>All-In After Loss</h3>
            <p>After my grandmother passed, I put everything into IT. Passed CCST Networking on the third attempt — which I needed to qualify for SkillsUSA. Started the CompTIA track immediately after.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="journey-entry milestone">
          <div class="journey-dot"><div class="journey-dot-inner"></div></div>
          <div class="journey-body">
            <span class="journey-date">March 2026 — Three Weeks</span>
            <h3>CompTIA Trifecta: A+, Network+, Security+</h3>
            <p>Studied with Professor Messer and YouTube. Passed A+ Core 1 and Core 2 in a single week, Network+ the week after, Security+ the week after that. Three industry certifications in three consecutive weeks.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="journey-entry">
          <div class="journey-dot"><div class="journey-dot-inner"></div></div>
          <div class="journey-body">
            <span class="journey-date">Early April 2026 — Lab Expansion</span>
            <h3>Dell R610 &amp; R410 — Two More Nodes</h3>
            <p>My mentor found two servers people were throwing out — a Dell R610 and R410. Added them to the Proxmox cluster alongside the IBM, forming a three-node setup.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="journey-entry milestone">
          <div class="journey-dot"><div class="journey-dot-inner"></div></div>
          <div class="journey-body">
            <span class="journey-date">April 2026 — State Level</span>
            <h3>SkillsUSA Florida Internetworking — 1st Place</h3>
            <p>Won first place in Internetworking at the SkillsUSA Florida State Competition — networking knowledge tested under pressure against peers from across the state. Qualified for SkillsUSA NLSC in Atlanta, GA.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="journey-entry milestone">
          <div class="journey-dot"><div class="journey-dot-inner"></div></div>
          <div class="journey-body">
            <span class="journey-date">April 2026 — CompTIA</span>
            <h3>CySA+ Passed</h3>
            <p>Added the Cybersecurity Analyst certification, completing the CompTIA CSAP stackable credential pathway on top of the trifecta.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="journey-entry milestone">
          <div class="journey-dot"><div class="journey-dot-inner"></div></div>
          <div class="journey-body">
            <span class="journey-date">April 2026 — Tampa, FL</span>
            <h3>CyberLaunch USF State Championship</h3>
            <p>Competed in Florida's largest state-sponsored high school CTF at the University of South Florida — hosted by Cyber Florida. Advanced from the November virtual qualifier to the in-person State Championship.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="journey-entry">
          <div class="journey-dot"><div class="journey-dot-inner"></div></div>
          <div class="journey-body">
            <span class="journey-date">2026 — Full Rack Build</span>
            <h3>Switch Refresh + Enclosed 4-Post Rack</h3>
            <p>Upgraded to a Cisco SG300-20 core and Netgear GS728TP PoE access switch in the enclosed 4-post rack. The lab moved to a full Gigabit fabric with better VLAN control and PoE capacity for access devices.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="journey-entry milestone">
          <div class="journey-dot"><div class="journey-dot-inner"></div></div>
          <div class="journey-body">
            <span class="journey-date">May 2026 — Network Architecture</span>
            <h3>Enterprise VLAN Segmentation — Flat to 10-VLAN Production</h3>
            <p>Redesigned the entire lab from a single flat network to a fully segmented 10-VLAN production design using role-based private subnets. Replaced legacy switches mid-migration, recovered Proxmox corosync quorum, migrated 30+ services to correct VLANs, rewrote DNS overrides, updated NPMplus backends, and deployed default-deny OPNsense firewall rules. The biggest infrastructure project to date.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="journey-entry">
          <div class="journey-dot"><div class="journey-dot-inner"></div></div>
          <div class="journey-body">
            <span class="journey-date">May 2026 — Security Engineering</span>
            <h3>OPNsense OIDC Bug Fix &amp; DNS Migration</h3>
            <p>Discovered a PHP SimpleXML iterator bug in the open-source os-oidc-devel plugin that silently hid the Authentik SSO login button. Applied a rootless fix via FreeBSD package tooling and the configd socket — without touching the live config. Simultaneously migrated all OPNsense service configs from hardcoded IPs to DNS names for resilience.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="journey-entry milestone">
          <div class="journey-dot"><div class="journey-dot-inner"></div></div>
          <div class="journey-body">
            <span class="journey-date">June 1–5, 2026 — Atlanta, GA</span>
            <h3>SkillsUSA NLSC Nationals — Internetworking</h3>
            <p>Competing at SkillsUSA NLSC in Atlanta — the national championship with 6,500+ state champions from across the country. Actively studying CCNA (targeting June–July 2026) and PenTest+. Open to junior networking, SOC, NOC, MSP, and IT support roles.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="back-link">
      <a href="/">&larr; Back to homepage</a>
    </div>

</BaseLayout>
